B.aeO=new A.jF("The core scripture verses of the Bhagavad Gita are recognized as public domain material. However, the custom UI compilation, software container code, visual themes, custom layouts, engineering logic, and original architectural content are the exclusive proprietary property of Satvik Technologies.",null)
B.aeP=new A.jF("Geeta Nexus is provided strictly for personal, non-commercial, spiritual, and intellectual study. You agree to interact with the system platform, its data nodes, and other community vectors lawfully, respectfully, and in perfect alignment with a clean, satvik lifestyle framework.",null)
